# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Desert Pulse — environment variables
#
# Copy this file to ".env" if you ever add configuration:  cp .env.example .env
# Your real ".env" is git-ignored and must never be committed.
# (Vite only exposes variables that start with VITE_ to the browser.)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# This app currently needs NO secrets and NO API keys.
#
# The Pulse help chatbot answers a fixed set of predefined questions entirely
# in the browser — there is no external API call, so nothing to configure here.
#
# This file is kept as a placeholder for future settings (for example, if you
# later add a backend to store survey responses, put its URL below):
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
